  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Sweetener</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><div><b>“</b><span>Is yum!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wolfgang\" title=\"Wolfgang\">Wolfgang</a></p>\n</div>\n<p><b>Sweetener</b> is one of the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food_Value\" title=\"Food Value\">Food Value</a>. There are 2 basic Sweetening <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">food</a> items in-game (3 in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/24px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a>). None of them can be cooked.\n</p><p><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Royal_Jelly\" title=\"Royal Jelly\">Royal Jelly</a> has a Sweetener value of 3, while <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honeycomb\" title=\"Honeycomb\">Honeycomb</a> only have an Sweetener value of 1.\n</p>\n<div><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honeycomb\" title=\"Honeycomb\"><img alt=\"Honeycomb\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honeycomb.png?56b468\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honeycomb\" title=\"Honeycomb\">Honeycomb</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Royal_Jelly\" title=\"Royal Jelly\"><img alt=\"Royal Jelly\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Royal_Jelly.png?7b823e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Royal_Jelly\" title=\"Royal Jelly\">Royal Jelly</a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/24px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Crock_Pot_Meals_that_require_Sweeteners\">Crock Pot Meals that require Sweeteners</span></h2>\n<div class=\"version-filters hidden\">\n<p><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/28px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"28\" height=\"31\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/28px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"28\" height=\"31\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/28px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"28\" height=\"31\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/28px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"28\" height=\"31\"></a>\n</p>\n</div>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\">Food\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"150px\">Name\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\">DLC\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Health_Icon.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Health\"><img alt=\"Health\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Health_Icon.png/28px-Health_Icon.png?1ec0e6\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Hunger_Icon.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Hunger\"><img alt=\"Hunger\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hunger_Icon.png/28px-Hunger_Icon.png?9d0486\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Sanity_Icon.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Sanity\"><img alt=\"Sanity\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Sanity_Icon.png/28px-Sanity_Icon.png?eae728\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rot.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Perish time (days)\"><img alt=\"Perish time (days)\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rot.png/28px-Rot.png?31f7bc\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Crock_Pot.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Cook time (sec)\"><img alt=\"Cook time (sec)\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/28px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Priority.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Priority\"><img alt=\"Priority\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Priority.png/24px-Priority.png?9a8804\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"></a>\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Recipe\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Requirements\n</th>\n<th>Filler<br>Restrictions\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>